      <title>法国总理作出让步争取时间通过预算案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/french-premier-buys-time-to-pass-budget-with-concessions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁 (Francois Bayrou) 提出重新谈判有争议的 2023 年养老金法，似乎为自己争取了至少几个月的执政时间，并确保获得足够多议员的默许支持以通过一项急需的预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/french-premier-buys-time-to-pass-budget-with-concessions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 19:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大内阁部长选择退出，卡尼与弗里兰争夺最高职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/carney-freeland-duel-for-top-job-as-canada-ministers-opt-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继任贾斯汀·特鲁多担任加拿大总理的竞选越来越像是前财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰和前央行行长马克·卡尼之间的双向战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/carney-freeland-duel-for-top-job-as-canada-ministers-opt-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 18:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《爱尔兰时报》称爱尔兰主要政党达成政府协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/ireland-s-main-parties-reach-government-deal-irish-times-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《爱尔兰时报》报道，经过数周的谈判，爱尔兰中间派政党达成协议，在少数不结盟议员的支持下组建联合政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/ireland-s-main-parties-reach-government-deal-irish-times-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 18:00:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普特别顾问 2020 年选举报告的关键要点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/key-takeaways-from-trump-special-counsel-2020-election-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前特别检察官杰克·史密斯 (Jack Smith) 为针对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的指控进行了有力的辩护，指控他参与了“前所未有的犯罪行为，以推翻 2020 年大选的合法结果”。以下是关键要点。]]></description>
