      <title>特朗普就职后几天将在达沃斯向精英发表演讲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/von-der-leyen-milei-to-attend-davos-as-trump-appears-on-screen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将在就任美国总统三天后在达沃斯发表线上演讲，这可能是世界经济论坛上最受关注的演讲之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/von-der-leyen-milei-to-attend-davos-as-trump-appears-on-screen</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 13:15:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
